: 14px; font-family: Muli, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(61, 70, 67); letter-spacing: normal;">Have you ever considered using avocado oil for dry scalp? A dry scalp is one of the most frustrating things you can deal with. It’s itching and irritating, it makes your hair look bad, and it can cause dandruff.</p></h1>', NULL, NULL, '359', '358|357', NULL, 514, NULL, NULL, 1, 'used', NULL, '+8801799328264', 0, 'Dhaka, Bangladesh', 23.7820624, 90.4160527, 1, 189, 1, 1, NULL, '2024-06-11 03:12:03', '2025-03-18 23:37:33', '2024-05-01 23:06:12', '2025-03-18 23:37:33'),
	(11, 1, NULL, 2, 10, NULL, 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Anker Sound Core R500 Bluetooth Headphone', 'anker-sound-core-r500-bluetooth-headphone', '<p>Experience unparalleled audio quality with the Anker Sound Core R500 Bluetooth Headphones. These headphones deliver crisp, clear sound with powerful bass, making them perfect for music lovers and audiophiles. Designed for ultimate comfort, they feature soft ear cups and an adjustable headband for a perfect fit. With up to 20 hours of playtime on a single charge, they are ideal for long listening sessions. Compatible with all Bluetooth-enabled devices, including smartphones, tablets, and laptops. Don\'t miss out on this fantastic deal – get your Anker Sound Core R500 today!<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '684', '685|683', NULL, 100, NULL, NULL, 1, 'new', 'original', '+8801799328264', 0, 'Dhaka, Bangladesh', 23.7947536, 90.4143085, 1, 459, 1, 1, NULL, '2024-06-11 03:12:03', '2025-03-18 23:37:25', '2024-05-01 23:11:06', '2025-03-18 23:37:25'),
	(13, 24, NULL, 50, NULL, 6, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Apple Reconditioned No Scratch Laptop', 'dell-reconditioned-no-scratch-laptop', 'Introducing the Mobvoi TicWatch Pro 3 Ultra GPS, the ultimate smartwatch that redefines performance and versatility. Powered by the latest Qualcomm Snapdragon Wear 4100 platform, it delivers lightning-fast performance and enhanced energy efficiency for seamless multitasking and extended battery life. With built-in Ultra GPS technology, this smartwatch provides precise location tracking and navigation, perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and fitness enthusiasts alike. Featuring a dual-layer display with AMOLED and FSTN panels, it offers exceptional clarity and visibility in any lighting condition while conserving battery life. The TicWatch Pro 3 Ultra GPS boasts a comprehensive suite of health and fitness tracking features, including heart rate monitoring, sleep tracking, and blood oxygen saturation measurement, empowering you to take control of your well-being. Stay connected on the go with notifications, calls, and apps directly from your wrist, making it the ultimate companion for your active lifestyle. Dive into a world of endless possibilities with the Mobvoi TicWatch Pro 3 Ultra GPS – where innovation meets performance.<br>', NULL, NULL, '983', '746|744|743|382', NULL, 145, NULL, NULL, 1, 'new', NULL, '+8801799328264', 0, 'ঢাকা, Bangladesh', 23.8040930, 90.4152376, 0, 194, 1, 1, NULL, '2025-03-18 23:54:17', NULL, '2024-05-08 08:19:38', '2025-03-20 14:07:59'),
	(14, 24, NULL, 51, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Mobvoi TicWatch Pro 3 Ultra GPS', 'mobvoi-ticwatch-pro-3-ultra-gps', 'Introducing the Mobvoi TicWatch Pro 3 Ultra GPS, the ultimate smartwatch that redefines performance and versatility. Powered by the latest Qualcomm Snapdragon Wear 4100 platform, it delivers lightning-fast performance and enhanced energy efficiency for seamless multitasking and extended battery life. With built-in Ultra GPS technology, this smartwatch provides precise location tracking and navigation, perfect for outdoor enthusiasts and fitness enthusiasts alike. Featuring a dual-layer display with AMOLED and FSTN panels, it offers exceptional clarity and visibility in any lighting condition while conserving battery life. The TicWatch Pro 3 Ultra GPS boasts a comprehensive suite of health and fitness tracking features, including heart rate monitoring, sleep tracking, and blood oxygen saturation measurement, empowering you to take control of your well-being. Stay connected on the go with notifications, calls, and apps directly from your wrist, making it the ultimate companion for your active lifestyle. Dive into a world of endless possibilities with the Mobvoi TicWatch Pro 3 Ultra GPS – where innovation meets performance.', NULL, NULL, '982', NULL, NULL, 250, NULL, NULL, 1, 'new', 'original', '+8801799328264', 0, 'Dhaka, Bangladesh', 23.8701988, 90.4233984, 1, 102, 1, 1, NULL, '2025-03-18 23:54:17', NULL, '2024-05-08 08:23:17', '2025-03-18 23:54:17'),
	(15, 24, NULL, 50, NULL, NULL, 5, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'EHS-18CRN|NEW Elite 1.5 Ton Split AC', 'ehs-18crn-new-elite-1-5-ton-split-ac', 'Introducing the EHS-18CRN, the latest addition to our Elite series of Split Air Conditioners, designed to redefine your cooling experience. With a powerful cooling capacity of 1.5 tons, this AC ensures efficient and effective cooling even in large spaces. Equipped with advanced features like Turbo Cooling and Sleep Mode, it offers customizable comfort to suit your preferences throughout the day and night. The sleek and modern design of the Elite series adds a touch of sophistication to any room décor. Experience whisper-quiet operation, thanks to its low noise levels, allowing you to relax without disturbance. With energy-saving capabilities, this AC not only keeps you cool but also reduces your electricity bills. Stay cool and comfortable all summer long with the EHS-18CRN Elite 1.5 Ton Split AC', NULL, NULL, '984', '406', NULL, 500, NULL, NULL, 1, 'new', 'original', '+8801799328264', 0, 'Dhaka, Bangladesh', 23.7931750, 90.4071831, 1, 244, 1, 1, NULL, '2025-03-18 23:54:17', NULL, '2024-05-08 08:24:18', '2025-03-19 14:18:04'),
