	(26, 'FaqOne', 'update', 'plugins\\PageBuilder\\Addons\\Faq\\FaqOne', 'dynamic_page', 1, 7, 'dynamic_page', '{"id":"26","addon_name":"FaqOne","addon_namespace":"cGx1Z2luc1xQYWdlQnVpbGRlclxBZGRvbnNcRmFxXEZhcU9uZQ==","addon_type":"update","addon_location":"dynamic_page","addon_order":"1","addon_page_id":"7","addon_page_type":"dynamic_page","title":"Frequently Asked Questions","contact_info":"Didn\\u2019t find the right answer? here you can ask your own questions to our support","contact_info_title":"Contact us","contact_info_link":"https:\\/\\/listocean.bytesed.com\\/contact","contact_page_contact_info_01":{"title_":["User Registration and Authentication","Listing Management","Search and Filter","Payment Integration","Messaging System","User Reviews and Ratings","Responsive Design:"],"description_":["Allow users to create accounts and login securely. This will enable them to manage their listings, save favorite listings, and receive notifications.","Provide a user-friendly interface for creating, editing, and deleting listings. Each listing should include details such as title, description, price, category, location, contact information, and optional images.","Implement robust search and filter options to help users find relevant listings quickly. Users should be able to filter by category, location, price range, date posted, and other relevant criteria.","If you plan to monetize your website, integrate payment gateways to facilitate transactions between buyers and sellers. This could include options for one-time payments, subscriptions, or featured listings.","Enable communication between buyers and sellers through an internal messaging system. This will allow users to ask questions, negotiate prices, and arrange meetings securely.","Implement a system for users to leave reviews and ratings for sellers and their listings. This will help build trust and credibility within your community.","Ensure your website is optimized for various devices, including desktops, laptops, tablets, and smartphones. A responsive design will provide a seamless user experience across all devices."]},"section_bg":null,"padding_top":"50","padding_bottom":"100"}', '2024-05-07 04:12:52', '2024-06-27 12:30:00'),
	(27, 'TextEditor', 'update', 'plugins\\PageBuilder\\Addons\\Common\\TextEditor', 'dynamic_page', 1, 5, 'dynamic_page', '{"id":"27","addon_name":"TextEditor","addon_namespace":"cGx1Z2luc1xQYWdlQnVpbGRlclxBZGRvbnNcQ29tbW9uXFRleHRFZGl0b3I=","addon_type":"update","addon_location":"dynamic_page","addon_order":"1","addon_page_id":"5","addon_page_type":"dynamic_page","text_editor":"<p><span style=\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;\\"><br><\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 18px;\\">Terms and Conditions<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\"><br><\\/span><\\/p><p>\\r\\n<\\/p><p><span style=\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">Welcome to Listocean!<\\/span><\\/p><p>\\r\\n<\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">These terms and conditions outline the rules and regulations for the use of Llistocean Website, located at Llistocean .\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">By accessing this website we assume you accept these terms and conditions. Do not continue to use listocean if you do not agree to take all of the terms and conditions stated on this page.\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">The following terminology applies to these Terms and Conditions, Privacy Statement and Disclaimer Notice and all Agreements: \\"Client\\", \\"You\\" and \\"Your\\" refers to you, the person log on this website and compliant to the Company\'s terms and conditions. \\"The Company\\", \\"Ourselves\\", \\"We\\", \\"Our\\" and \\"Us\\", refers to our Company. \\"Party\\", \\"Parties\\", or \\"Us\\", refers to both the Client and ourselves. All terms refer to the offer, acceptance and consideration of payment necessary to undertake the process of our assistance to the Client in the most appropriate manner for the express purpose of meeting the Client\'s needs in respect of provision of the Company\'s stated services, in accordance with and subject to, prevailing law of Netherlands. Any use of the above terminology or other words in the singular, plural, capitalization and\\/or he\\/she or they, are taken as interchangeable and therefore as referring to same.\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">Cookies\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">We employ the use of cookies. By accessing listocean, you agreed to use cookies in agreement with the listocean Privacy Policy.\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">Most interactive websites use cookies to let us retrieve the user\'s details for each visit. Cookies are used by our website to enable the functionality of certain areas to make it easier for people visiting our website. Some of our affiliate\\/advertising partners may also use cookies.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\"><br><\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">License\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">Unless otherwise stated, Llistocean and\\/or its licensors own the intellectual property rights for all material on Llistocean. All intellectual property rights are reserved. You may access this from Llistocean for your own personal use subjected to restrictions set in these terms and conditions.<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\"><br><\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\">\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: normal; background-color: rgb