	(41, 'site_meta_description', 'Dive into the endless possibilities of buying and selling at ListOcean! Navigate a vast sea of opportunities as you connect with buyers and sellers effortlessly. Uncover incredible deals on a wide range of items or transform your unused items into treasure by listing them for sale. Immerse yourself in our dynamic community and enjoy the simplicity of buying and selling. Begin your oceanic journey today at ListOcean – where opportunities flow like waves!', '2023-12-13 05:24:59', '2024-06-22 00:10:19'),
